      "body": "Since no one else is reporting the problem this is very likely something on your end, most likely the browser - as depressing as that sounds...\n\nYou can start disabling add-ons and extensions and you may find the issue but it might be better to do a complete reinstall of Chrome then add any extensions etc back in and check each time between add-ons.\n\nAlternately you could install Firefox and make sure that is working \"out of the box\" before you start tearing things up....  \n\nI take it you are having no other issues with other sites?",
